701191f-a.title: Bronx: Grand Concourse - 205th Street (East)
701191f-a.text:
3135-3133 Grand Concourse, at the S.W. corner of East 205th Street.
The street extending towards the background from where the horse and
Wagon are standing is East 205th Street.
May 8, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
